Anyway, patch available:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=eribeiro&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;eribeiro&quot;&gt;eribeiro&lt;/a&gt;, can you please verify that this works?&lt;/p&gt;

